So you can modify it a little bit, right?

00:51:19.520 --> 00:51:24.239
So now suddenly it looks like a bunch of function tools, right?

00:51:24.239 --> 00:51:29.199
So you could modify the input to turn it into what looks like a bunch of R function tools,

00:51:30.000 --> 00:51:35.360
define the functions R and L that does what we need.

00:51:36.239 --> 00:51:37.919
And then evaluate the input.

